```

In this example, we've used `multiply` blend mode on the circle element to make it blend in with the background. We've also added an animation to make the circle pulse in and out, which creates a dynamic and eye-catching effect. As you can see, there are many creative ways to use blend modes in web design. By experimenting with different blend modes and design elements, you can create unique and visually stunning effects that enhance the overall look and feel of your website.

